  "title": "Architect (Commercial Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Project Nature: Mixed-Development, Civic and Downtown with Middle-East experience (role is based in Singapore office with travelling responsibilities required)</li><li>Conceptualizes concept and schematic designs</li><li>Execute feasibility studies and presents design proposals</li><li>Preparation of tender documentation, schedules and specifications</li><li>Liaises and discuss project-relevant issues with clients</li><li>Liaises and coordinates with consultants and contractors</li><li>Ensures design quality and authority compliance</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Architecture</li><li>Minimum 3-5 Years of relevant architectural experience, in relevant discipline, with a background working on middle-east based projects</li><li>Please attach sample portfolio of works together with your application</li></ul><p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong></p><p>Dickson KOH, EA Registration R1103367</p><p>www.bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
